== 当代用法 ==
现在，巴基斯坦用“西旁遮普”一词指代除拉合尔/中部地区之外的整个巴基斯坦旁遮普省，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/weekly/herald/herald18.htm |title=The political divides within – Dawn |accessdate=2016-11-22 |archive-date=2008-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007014658/http://dawn.com/weekly/herald/herald18.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>而在印度该词仍被用来指代整个巴基斯坦旁遮普省。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://punjabgovt.nic.in/CULTURE/Excavated.htm |title=Excavated Sites – Government of Punjab (India) |access-date=2016-11-22 |archive-date=2008-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081101180130/http://punjabgovt.nic.in/Culture/Excavated.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

